        <speech by="#40342c81-d15f-4412-9e39-be7ba9a478a9">
          <from>HON. MAUREEN MACDONALD</from>
          <p>HON. MAUREEN MACDONALD : Mr. Speaker, my question is for the Premier. In January, the Minister of Labour and Advanced Education wrote a letter to approximately 60 organizations that provide job training and skills development for persons with disabilities here in Nova Scotia, warning that their funding was about to be cut off because of a funding decision in Ottawa.</p>
